3 teaspoons shelled roasted pistachio nuts, divided
des: "Sweet and salty come together in this peach and pistachio-flavored yogurt cup."
ins: Remove 1 tablespoon yogurt from yogurt container. Stir in 1 tablespoon of the diced peaches and 2 teaspoons of the pistachio nuts. Top with the remaining peaches and pistachios. Enjoy!
